## ğŸ”§ Developer Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Av-sek/api-profiler.git
cd api_profiler
pip install -e .

# OR build and install from source
pip install --upgrade build
python -m build
pip install dist/api_profiler-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl
```

To use on your Django app:

```bash
profile run
```

